{"tid":1270262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急]今天天氣預測","createTime":"2019-06-30T21:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T23:04:46.000Z","uid":62151,"like":200,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"1560d105eec014361909923997471848da2967d8","tid":1270262,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T21:12:35.000Z","msg":"首先同大家分析一下風向<br />\n而家香港打緊東南風<br />\n簡單一啲講即係<span style=\"color: red;\">所有野都會飛曬去西北方向</span><br />\n<br />\n另外 雨雲亦不斷形成<br />\n相信<span style=\"color: red;\">今日大部份時間都會落雨</span><br />\n大幅<span style=\"color: red;\">降低空氣污染同異味</span><br />\n能見度都會降低 請各位做好防雨操施<br />\n<br />\n綜合以上，假如市民呼吸道有問題，<span style=\"color: red;\">面向西北方向移動</span>嘅話<br />\n空氣污染好有可能<span style=\"color: red;\">唔會對您做成任何影響</span><br />\n<br />\n最後都提醒一下大家小心地滑，<span style=\"color: red;\">注意安全</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1953c4a28edc7fd4b3c87677817e00379da840a6","tid":1270262,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T21:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659631c9b826b2f83a0ca16323909f2b5cd7e2a6","tid":1270262,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T21:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a077b4f110784b3b5e6f4ccebeb2045351e9f3d","tid":1270262,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T21:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a88fe95edaac7516692e33a461553fa432cc8f","tid":1270262,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T21:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605f3550f294784b167f5c0f81f804b1449ab25e","tid":1270262,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"c